==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Contraremonstrant
<hw>Con"tra*re*mon"strant</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who
remonstrates in opposition or answer to a remonstrant.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>They did the synod wrong to make this distinction of
<qex>contraremonstrants</qex> and remonstrants.</q>
<rj><qau>Hales.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>contrarian</ent>⟦br⟧
